history.content:
Check https://eecs.berkeley.edu/events -- I don't know that it will have all the tabling events, but it should have most info-sessions.

Also you can subscribe to the mailing list of company events. The below line is from an e-mail I got last year from Nicole about how to do this:

"Email <sympa@lists.eecs.berkeley.edu> with subscribe eecs-ugrads-jobs in the body of the message to receive information about EECS specific job posting and recruitment events."

Finally, some events will be mentioned in the Engineering Newsletter (e.g Twitter’s booth outside Bechtel). You could also check Handshake thought I’m not sure what if any events are posted there only.
